title: Here’s What Kylie Jenner, Keith Ape & A$AP Ferg Wore to Alexander Wang’s FW17 Show
text:
Visit the original post to see all 23 images from this gallery. 
Last night, a who’s who of fashion and celebrity elite trekked all the way to Harlem to catch Alexander Wang’s FW17 show. As one of the most anticipated events on New York Fashion Week’s calendar, stylish getups and lens-baiting peacocking were commonplace (as were the blinding strobes of flash photography that illuminated the streets once attendees stepped outside).
Here you’ll notice a few familiar faces, including Kylie Jenner, her sister Kendall (who walked in the show), A$AP Ferg, Teyana Taylor, Keith Ape, Luka Sabbat and more.
What do you think of the Wang Gang’s outfit choices? How does they fare against the street style at VFILES’s show ?
For more coverage of FW17 Fashion Week be sure to read our other reports on today’s hottest brands .
